OL,7,FAlex Eades and her daughter Charlotte
OL,8,Fdid everything together - whether it
OL,9,Fwas shopping, or trying new make-up,
OL,10,Fthe pair were inseparable.
OL,12,FCharlotte Eades was 16 when she was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with a glioblastoma
OL,14,Fmultiforme, a fast-growing and rare
OL,15,Fform of brain cancer.
OL,17,FDuring her illness, Charlotte fought
OL,18,Fto raise awareness of cancer in young
OL,19,Fpeople and kept a video blog to
OL,20,Fdocument her gruelling treatment and
OL,21,Fthe side effects.
