OL,7,FCharlotte died in 2016, a week after
OL,8,Fher 19th birthday.
OL,10,FFollowing Charlotte's death, her mum
OL,11,FAlex became determined to continue her
OL,12,Flegacy.
OL,14,FAnd nine years on, Alex has raised
OL,15,Fhundreds of thousands of pounds for
OL,16,FGlioblastoma research and awareness.
OL,18,F"To see your child deteriorate, to see
OL,19,Fyour son lose his sister and suddenly
OL,20,Fbecome an only child, it's devastating.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
