OL,7,F"I was very close to Charlotte - we
OL,8,Fdid everything together, we did
OL,9,Fshopping, we drank wine, we watched
OL,10,Ffilms - everything.
OL,12,F"And suddenly no more."
OL,14,FCharlotte, along with Alex and her
OL,15,Fbrother Miles, established the charity
OL,16,FCharlotte's BAG, which stands for
OL,17,FCharlotte's Battle Against
OL,18,FGlioblastoma, and also a nod to her
OL,19,Flove of handbags.
