OL,7,FThe charity has donated around
OL,8,F#250,000 to King's College Hospital in
OL,9,FLondon, contributing significantly to
OL,10,Fthe brain tumour service.
OL,12,FThe money has been spent developing a
OL,13,Flaboratory, employing a scientist in
OL,14,Fneuropathology to help with whole
OL,15,Fgenome sequencing of children with
OL,16,Fbrain tumours.
