OL,7,FAlex's friend Domenica Maxted said:
OL,8,F"She lost her child, her beloved
OL,9,Fdaughter, yet she's dedicated her life
OL,10,Fto raising awareness of this illness,
OL,11,Fof glioblastoma, and funding research
OL,12,Finto it.
OL,14,F"What she's done is really just
OL,15,Fincredible.
OL,17,F"I'm so proud of her."
